# 📊 TaxPal - Accounting Made Simple

TaxPal is a modern, responsive landing page designed for a small business accounting SaaS (Software as a Service) platform. It features a clean UI, pricing tables, testimonials, and a mobile-friendly design.

## 🚀 Live Demo
You can view the live website here: 
[https://dilikshanamalshan-cloud.github.io/tax-pal/](https://dilikshanamalshan-cloud.github.io/tax-pal/)

## ✨ Features
* **Modern Hero Section:** Eye-catching design to grab user attention.
* **Responsive Layout:** Fully optimized for Mobile, Tablet, and Desktop views.
* **Tailwind CSS:** Styled using the latest Tailwind utility classes for a sleek look.
* **Pricing Plans:** Clearly defined tiers for different business needs.
* **Testimonials & FAQ:** Built-in sections for social proof and customer support.

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
* **HTML5:** Structure of the web page.
* **Tailwind CSS:** For modern and fast styling (via CDN).
* **GitHub Pages:** For free hosting and deployment.

